{"tid":584073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習總稱帝首談修憲：過程充分發揚民主","createTime":"2018-03-07T14:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T06:41:24.000Z","uid":3393,"like":12,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"9611d2d005406ebf4b2b51db2c0ae97bc179e0d7","tid":584073,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"今日上午，中共中央總書記習近平參加廣東代表團審議。央視新聞聯播晚上報道習近平在會上的講話內容，當中包括習近平首次開腔談中央修憲的提議。<br />\n<br />\n習近平表示，完全贊同憲法修正案草案，強調對中國現行憲法作部份修改，是黨中央從新時代堅持和發展中國特色社會主義全局和戰略高度作出的重大決策，也是推進全面依法治國、推進國家治理體系和治理能力現代化的重大舉措。憲法修正案草案在形成過程中充分發揚了民主，集中了各方面智慧，體現了黨和人民的共同意志。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180307/57914156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180307%2F57914156&d=dANmUINyULLXl1SVtOyhv7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=44a042f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180307%2F57914156&h=6695f8db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180307/57914156</a>"},{"pid":"540afb8a7b6667f02c8c335c86b662202f80a727","tid":584073,"uid":41375,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/65618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F65618.jpg&h=d76a7d24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a08c4e2daa7759f147b59585e636a53daa950e28","tid":584073,"uid":26156,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:28:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9382914b490187c2eac8c3519b902117ff59ad9","tid":584073,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"趙高"},{"pid":"4c125e85cfc57982652b993e4f7a18194213fc95","tid":584073,"uid":68285,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse